Looking at your class the following tests spring to mind:

getPage: valid path, null path, invalid path, path to enormous file, 
path to zero byte file
addPage: paths as for getPage tests, null page, valid page (and all 
combinations thereof...)

You&#39;ll need some way to make a Document and a Page in memory to test 
this correctly - presumably some kind of mock.

Just as important is the fact that by adding just one test to this class 
you would then have the testing framework set up - which is useful for 
testing any other classes you add.

(As an aside, I&#39;d make the HashMap &quot;pages&quot; a Map instead - it&#39;s a little 
more flexible that way...)

HTH,
Jim Cheesman



